# OpenTofu Module Builder Skill

Created: 2026-02-27
Purpose: Build production-ready OpenTofu/Terraform AWS modules following terraform-modules repository patterns

## Structure
- SKILL.md: Main workflow and instructions
- references/module-patterns.md: Coding patterns from existing modules
- references/aws-best-practices.md: Security defaults and AWS-specific guidance

## Usage
This skill triggers when creating new infrastructure modules, refactoring existing modules, or extending module capabilities for AWS resources.

## Key Features
- Step-by-step module creation workflow
- Security-first defaults
- Validation patterns
- Testing guidance
- README templates with terraform-docs integration
- Dynamic block patterns
- Module complexity guidelines
